{
  "stem": "18470.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So no matter what, you know, unreasonableness that was attached to this libel, it made no difference with the expression of violence.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the beatings sometimes were pretty bad.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So after a while, Werner's Day I never left the house.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Now what is unusual [SIGHS] in some respects is that when my wife and I went to Germany about 10 years ago, I took her on a visit through the town.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I hear by the wall, which was a passageway to one end of town, a mass going on.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And it was a mass to-- it was Werner's Day.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there was a mass to the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I went in to look at it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the wall, which I'd never seen-- if had seen it was a child, I didn't remember it-- depicted the entire alleged incident.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when the Pope visited America in Miami, I happened to be sitting at the night of a festive dinner at the table of Cardinal Hildebrand's, who was in charge of Jewish-Christian relations.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I told him what I had seen and heard.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He said, it's impossible.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We desacralized Werner.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "All ritual murders where desacralized.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I said, but Cardinal, I saw it and heard it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He said, it's impossible.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I have a letter that he wrote me a month later, in which he said it's-- it was not only possible, it is still being practiced.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He has commanded or ordered that it be stopped.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But I will bet you dollars to donuts if we went to Oberwesel on the next Werner's Day, the mass would be recited.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So I believe that this kind of residual anti-Semitism is built into the fabric of that society.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And these legends don't die so quickly.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And you can outlaw them.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
